 * ║    for each. Saves up to 50× uncached meta reads per 2-minute                   ║
 * ║    retry cron tick. Non-behavioral — just warm cache.                           ║
 * ║  Version: V.2.3 — Phase 2 audit DB-H7 + DB-H8:                                ║
 * ║    (DB-H7) `b2f_run_diff_detection` now gated on                              ║
 * ║    `b2f_flag_shadow_write`. When Phase 3 cut-over is live                     ║
 * ║    + shadow_write disabled, cron early-exits — avoids ~3K                     ║
 * ║    ACF reads/hr on Phase 3+ systems where CPT ≈ junction.                     ║
 * ║    (DB-H8) `b2f_run_observations_ttl` chunks DELETE — 1000                    ║
 * ║    rows/iter + 50ms gap × 20 max iterations (mirror Snippet                   ║
 * ║    16 attempt-log cleanup pattern). Prevents table lock minutes                ║
